headline: Goldman Sachs cuts Bumble on weak turnaround visibility and stiff competition
summary: Investing.com -- Goldman Sachs downgraded Bumble Inc to Neutral from Buy and cut price target to $7 from $8, saying visibility into a turnaround at the core Bumble app is low and likely not forthcoming until mid-2026.
